Hate typing the same thing over and over, one key at a time?

Personalize and pre-program your keyboard with WordBoard. Now you can control what the keys input. Add a key to automatically type your email address, postal address, hashtag, an email template reply, ASCII art or anything else you can imagine.

"Perfect!"
"The app I now can't live without."

WordBoard can automatically import your recently used hashtags from Twitter and Instagram and also automatically create buttons for emails, phone numbers and addresses from your contacts.

Save time, type smarter and faster with WordBoard.

Download from the App Store : https://itunes.apple.com/us/app/wordboard-keyboard/id960167417?mt=8&ct=wbyt&at=11l4LZ